The paper discusses information hiding techniques and their potential impact on the iOS operating system. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning algorithms to detect information hiding, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact on Siri, which is a software engineering topic (cs.SE) and could also fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI) due to the communication aspect of the information hiding techniques.
